  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-1 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: all 13 factors assessed and meeting required levels. Complete-profile package with full provenance, UQ, and sensitivity analysis.",
